@startuml
title Video Suggestion System State Machine
[*] --> ReceiveRequest

state ReceiveRequest
ReceiveRequest : entry / receive video suggestion request from user
ReceiveRequest : do / identify user who made request
ReceiveRequest : exit / identified user

state GatherVideos
GatherVideos : entry / gather different types of videos based on user's profile or preferences
GatherVideos : do / gather trending videos from user’s area, videos with similar tags, videos from similar genres, and promoted videos
GatherVideos : exit / gathered videos

state AddDetails
AddDetails : entry / add additional details such as thumbnails and view counts to suggested videos
AddDetails : do / add details
AddDetails : exit / added details

state SendSuggestedVideos
SendSuggestedVideos : entry / send suggested videos to user
SendSuggestedVideos : do / send videos
SendSuggestedVideos : exit / sent videos

ReceiveRequest --> GatherVideos
GatherVideos --> AddDetails
AddDetails --> SendSuggestedVideos
SendSuggestedVideos --> [*]

@enduml
